                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7150" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0715</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7609 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“扶”农到“服”农：锦泰期货助力乡村振兴实践探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> From “Supporting” to “Serving”: Practical exploration on Rural Revitalization by Jintai Futures Limited Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">卞曰瑭，林月月，戎麾，徐壮丽，韩丽亚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> 锦泰期货有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融扶贫；金融创新；渐进性创新；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial poverty alleviation; Financial innovation; Incremental innovation; Rural vitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融是我国巩固脱贫攻坚成果、有效防止返贫的根本保障，是我国实现农业农村现代化发展的关键力量，更是支持乡村振兴战略、实现共同富裕的“源头活水”。本案例描述了锦泰期货深入剖析农村金融供需错位的现实问题根源，积极探索金融支持农业农村现代化建设的生动实践。以国家推动“保险+期货”助力金融扶贫政策为契机，锦泰期货积极协同各类金融机构延伸服务内涵和外延，构建“保险+期货+X”为核心特色金融产品保障脱贫攻坚，并努力深度衔接金融支持乡村振兴战略。伴随锦泰期货助力“三农”的金融服务内涵持续深化，分别从开发专业化金融产品、提供一站式金融服务、设计高效率运营方式等维度，全面打造出三位一体“锦泰模式”支撑乡村振兴。面临疫情防控常态化和数字经济发展趋势，锦泰期货力求借助“锦泰模式”成功实践，进一步探索数字金融服务乡村振兴转型升级，真正实现金融“扶农”向“服农”的高质量发展。通过本案例的学习，旨在引导学员理解金融创新的本质内涵，系统探究金融机构服务实体经济模式创新的渐进性实现过程逻辑，同时进一步探索金融创新在助推乡村振兴战略的实践应用，为金融企业助推“三农”发展现代化提供借鉴和启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Finance is the fundamental guarantee for China to consolidate the achievements of poverty alleviation and prevent poverty return effectively, and is the key force to realize the modernization of agricultural and rural, which is also like the inflowing water from its source to support the Rural Revitalization Strategy and achieve ultimate goal of common prosperity. In this case, the vivid practice of Jintai Futures Limited Company is deeply described, which focuses on analyzing the mismatch problem of rural finance between its supply and demand. Taking the opportunity of the national policy of promoting the financial support for poverty alleviation by applying the mode of “insurance + futures”, Jintai futures actively cooperates with other financial institutions to extend its service connotation by adopting the model of “insurance + futures +X”, so as to connect the strategy of financial support for Rural Revitalization deeply. With the deepening of the financial service connotation to help “agriculture, rural areas and farmers”, a trinity “Jintai model” of providing financial service to support rural revitalization has been comprehensively established from the following three dimensions, comprising developing specialized financial products, providing One-Stop financial services, and designing efficient operation patterns. Facing epidemic prevention and control and the development of digital economy, Jintai Futures Limited Company strives to explore the transformation and upgrading of digital financial services for Rural Revitalization with the help of the successful practice of “Jintai model”, so as to truly realize the high-quality development from “supporting agriculture” to “serving agriculture”. In this case, the purpose is to guide the students to understand the essential connotation of financial innovation, and to explore the gradual realization process of financial innovation and how it works in serving the real economy systematically, especially its application in promoting the Rural Revitalization Strategy, so that it should provide reference and enlightenment for financial enterprises to promote the development and modernization of “agriculture, rural areas and farmers”.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> 《金融创新》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业选择创新的影响因素；金融创新的内涵及外延；金融创新如何服务“三农”；金融机构进行渐进性创新的过程逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
